{"tid":2264522,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邱騰華現身BBC  指香港會維持亞洲金融中心的地位","createTime":"2020-10-30T16:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T16:57:29.000Z","uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"208eca5d781f954c36442f397171904d3c146456","tid":2264522,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:47:52.000Z","msg":"香港是亞洲金融中心，人口超過七百萬人。它是進入作為世界第二大經濟體中國的一個城市。不過，2019年下半年數個月的社會動蕩及北京訂立的《香港國安法》，為這個城市的身份帶來危機。以堅韌性和企業精神聞名的香港，能否保持它作為環球金融中心的地位？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-54730231.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-54730231.amp&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdiwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=e128b3c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-54730231.amp&h=feedd0a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-54730231.amp</a>"},{"pid":"aaf42def0c1f0c831662f6b77f0b53cec60dfcf3","tid":2264522,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:57:29.000Z","msg":"基本法腐乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}